name: Antarctic Krill Oil 500mg Omega 3 Fatty Acid Supplement, MegaRed Extra Strength EPA & DHA Softgels (90cnt box), Antioxidant Astaxanthin, Heart Health Supplement With No Fish Oil Aftertaste
feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Krill is one of the world’s most abundant and sustainable organisms. MegaRed only sources krill from the Antarctic where krill is most abundant.,OMEGA 3 SUPPLEMENT: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil has been shown to significantly increase your omega 3 index in just 30 days. Supportive research has shown that consumption of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids may reduce the risk of coronary heart disease.,HEART HEALTH: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil supplements provide an optimal combination of omega-3 fatty acids and the powerful antioxidant astaxanthin to support heart health in a once daily softgel.,3X MORE PURE: MegaRed with PureTechTM is 3x MORE PURE than regular krill oil. Salts and other impurities are removed to provide the purest krill oil on the market.,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE and EASY ABSORPTION: Krill Oil is carried in a phospholipid form which is better absorbed by the human body and because it's krill oil as opposed to fish oil, MegaRed Krill Oil has no fishy aftertaste or odor.,These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

feature_bullets: KRILL OIL DOUBLE STRENGTH FORMULA - Blossom Nature's formula contains Krill Oil 1600mg, Astaxanthin 2mg,EPA 174mg, DHA 120mg, Phospholipids 550mg. Each bottle contains 120 tablets of premium quality Organic Beet Root enhanced with Organic Black Pepper.,MONEY BACK GUARANTEE - 30 Days unconditional money back guarantee. We want you to be fully satisfied. If Beet Root or Krill Oil does not work for you, please send it back and get your money back.

name: Omega Krill Oil, Food Supplement for Brain, Heart and Joint Support, Helps Manage Cholesterol Levels, Made of Pure Krill and Enriched with Omega 3, 6 and 9, 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: Pure Krill Supplement - Get your daily dose of omega 3 oil with these vitamins. Our proprietary, antioxidant-rich krill oil omega 3 contains essential, naturally-occurring fatty acids. These nutrients benefit many bodily functions and help manage cholesterol levels.,Ideal Fish Oil Alternative - Instead of a fish oil omega 3 supplement, go for our omega 3 krill oil. Our krill ingredient is sustainably sourced from the pristine Antarctic waters. So, you can enjoy the full benefits of marine nutrients without the fishy aftertaste.,Supports Heart Function - Keeping your heart in shape is a breeze with Omega Krill. Like fish oil omega 3 supplements, ours is enriched with Omega3, 6 and 9. Formulated for enhanced absorption, it works in synergy with Astaxanthin to promote optimum heart function.,Easy-to-Swallow Capsules - Omega red krill oil dietary supplements come in soft gel form, so they’re easy to take and are quickly absorbed by the body. Take 1-2 capsules with a meal daily or as advised by your wellness provider.,All-Natural Krill Oil Vitamin - These vitamin supplements are derived from crustacean shellfish. Non-GMO and lactose-free, they have no artificial colors and preservatives. (Not suitable for vegetarians and those with adverse reactions to shellfish).
